m_q.target_metric: Compare the arrival order of Tony Maggs and Jo Siffert in the race
sub_questions: What were the finishing positions of Tony Maggs and Jo Siffert?
Which driver had the lower position number (indicating earlier arrival)?

scale_issues: Time/Retired column contains mixed data types: time durations (e.g., '2.02:58.6') and retirement reasons (e.g., 'Engine')

format_notes: Missing values in Pos column are represented by empty strings
Time/Retired column contains both time values and retirement reasons

constraints: Pos values should be integers for finished drivers
Grid values should be integers between 1 and starting grid size
derived_filters: Pos not null (to filter out retired drivers)
statistical_tests: Compare Pos values for the two drivers
output_format_requirements: Return driver name who came earlier
If both retired, compare lap counts from Time/Retired column
